  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Half board includes breakfast and dinner. There are nine restaurants at Chia Laguna Resort, each using fresh, local ingredients to create recipes inspired by traditional Sardinian cuisine. For a supplement, you can upgrade to the Dine Around programme, allowing you to try a different restaurant each evening.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
