  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Hotel Baia is the newest addition to the superb Chia Laguna Resort. With chic Mediterranean-style rooms and wonderful views over Chia’s splendid beach, this hotel is ideal for couples looking to get away from it all. The resort sits at the foot of the mountains in South Sardinia, close to some of the most picturesque beaches on the island, where a seemingly-endless stretch of white sand leads to crystal-clear waters.</span></p>
<p><span>The hotel’s infinity pool is equipped with comfy loungers and surrounded by nature. A poolside bar and relaxed restaurant offer a creative menu of refreshing drinks and regional cuisine. For those that want to truly unwind, head to the resort’s impressive spa where you’ll find a large choice of treatments as well as several swimming pools. With a choice of ten restaurants (open seasonally) and numerous bars, you’ll be spoilt for choice when it comes to romantic evenings. A dine around programme is available for a supplement if you want to try them all.</span></p>
<p><span>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Chia Laguna Resort - Hotel Baia is approx. 1 hour from Cagliari airport.</span></p>]]></description>
