  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><em>The newest hotel at Chia Laguna Resort, Hotel Baia is nestled among the gardens that lead down towards the beach.</em></p>
<p><strong>Presitge Parco Rooms </strong>are about 26m² and sleep 1 - 3 people with a double bed and single divan bed. They have been finished in a modern style with light colours and exposed beams. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Prestige Laguna Rooms </strong>are about 26m² and sleep 1 - 3 people with a double bed and a single divan bed. They have a furnished patio with views over the lagoon.<span> These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </span></p>
<p><strong>Prestige Mare Rooms</strong> are about 26m² and sleep 1 - 3 people with a double bed and a single divan bed. They enjoy unforgettable sea views and have exposed wooden beams and and modern Mediterranean decor. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>are about 44-54m² and sleep up to 4 adults and a child's cot with a sleeping area with a double bed and a living area with a divan bed for two people. They are just a stones throw away from the sea and lagoon and views over the Chia sea from every room. Guests staying in the suite or suite Incanto get one complimentary Bioaquam circuit included per day per full paying adult. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Suite Incanto </strong>are about 140m² and sleep 2 - 4 people. They are perched in a unique clifftop location. The suite includes two double rooms with en suite bathrooms (one is about 45m² and the other is about 53m²). The rooms are joined by a large living room and outside there is a garden area with a shaded veranda. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
